On-Campus


Technical Helpdesk






Technical Helpdesk
Formerly known as "C-Stop"
Get support from one of our knowledgeable consultants for help with Accounts/Passwords, UIC-WiFi, Printing, Duo 2-Factor Authentication (2FA), software installations, and other university technology services.

Walk-in support is available at the IDEA Commons located in the Richard J. Daley Library Monday through Friday. See hours of operation below.

To schedule a virtual appointment for support with the Helpdesk team, visit it.uic.edu/schedule-support







            Technical Helpdesk
          Heading link



 
Copy link







Tech Support
Speak with one of our knowledgeable consultants for help with:

Accounts/Passwords
UIC Wireless Network
Personal Device Maintenance
Duo 2-Factor Authentication (2FA)
WebStore software installations
Technology Solutions services


Short-Term Equipment Lending
Short-term loans of various equipment to support the academic needs of students.




